description:
Join MacKenzie Drebit and Matt Schanche on Truth Matters as they challenge misconceptions about Seventh-day Adventist beliefs, particularly regarding the observance of the Seventh-day Sabbath. Discover how SDA beliefs are rooted in the moral law of the Ten Commandments, not the ceremonial law of Moses. Explore the belief that keeping the commandments is an expression of righteousness by faith, not works. Join us in exploring the timeless relevance of the old and new covenants and their significance today. Let's seek truth together in our exploration of Biblical truth.
